Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Combine the pineapple (with juice/ liquids), SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, lemon juice and dry mustard in a small bowl. Mix all together. Place chicken breasts in a lightly greased 9x13 inch baking dish. Spread the pineapple mixture over the chicken. Bake in the preheated oven for 50 to 60 minutes.